name: DaysIlivedonearth
0: ”Alexa, launch days I lived on earth”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: days i lived on earth
des:
This features helps you to find how many days old are you. If the year is not provided by default Alexa will consider the current or future year.

You can also try the following

Sample:
User: Alexa, lauch the days I lived on earth
Alexa: Rait for response from alexa.
User: 
Examples:
1. How many days I spent on earth
2. Just say your date of birth in the format "21st April 1993"
